headlines.headline: Tiraamp karoora Ameerikaan talaallii argachuuf qabatte himan

promo.summary: Piroojektiin 'Operation Warp Speed' jedhamu xumura bara kanaatti talaallii koronaavaayirasii argachuuf karoorfate.

media.title: Trump outlines plans for coronavirus vaccine

synopses.short: Trump outlines plans for coronavirus vaccine
synopses.long:
The US president elaborated on Operation Warp Speed, which aims to expedite vaccine development.

On Friday, President Trump announced that Moncef Slaoui,  former vaccine chief at GlaxoSmithKline and Gustave Perna, a four star general, would oversee the initiative, which was first reported in April. 

The president said that the operation's aim is to deliver a vaccine by the end of the year, if not by early 2021. 
While the vaccine trial process is notoriously arduous and risky, Trump said that the administration was moving at '"speed". 

Experts have cast doubt on the White House timelines for a jab.

At the press briefing, he insisted that the country would begin to reopen "vaccine or no vaccine".
synopses.medium: The US president elaborated on Operation Warp Speed, which aims to expedite vaccine development.
